	           @{" COPYRIGHT David Griffin And Alex Aris " Link "CopyrightTxt"}

We, The Creators Of "Coin Mania", Hope That You Will Enjoy Playing This Game
Almost As Much As We Have Enjoyed Making It. There Is Only One Consideration
That We  Hope You Will  Have In Mind When Playing This Game And That Is That
You Are Not Using  A Copy Off Someone Else. @{" Pirates " Link "Pirates"} Have Their Reasons For
Copying Software, But They Have Absolutely No Reason To Copy This Game, It is
@{" Cheapware " Link "Cheapware"}, Cheap !  If They Think It Is Rubbish, They
Will Only Have Wasted Ł5.00 Not Ł25.00.

		    @{" Click Here To Go To The MAIN MENU " Link "Main Menu"}
