Memory Requirements : 1 Meg Minimum.If You Have Over 1 Meg Of Memory Then You
                      Will  Have The Ability To Store More Information,   But
                      It Depends On The Type Of Free Memory i.e Chip Or Fast.

Disk Requirements   : 1 Floppy Disk Or 1 Hard Disk. A Hard Disk  Installer Is
		      Supplied With Coin Mania.

