@Node "TroubleTxt" "Coinmania.Guide/Trouble Shooting"

	  ###### #####   ####  ##  ## #####  ##      #####
	    ##   ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##     ##
	    ##   ###### ##  ## ##  ## #####  ##     ######
	    ##   ## ##  ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##
	    ##   ##  ## ###### ###### ###### ###### ######
	    ##   ##  ## ###### ###### ###### ###### ######
	    ##   ##  ##  ####   ####  #####   ####   ##### SHOOTING

	     Problem				 Answer
	     				
Computer Keeps Asking For The
Volume "CoinMania".		Check For The Assign In Your "User-StartUp"
				If The Game Is On Your Hard Disk Else If On
				Floppy Check The Disk Is Called "CoinMania"
				If you cannot find the problem then install
				Coin Mania again using the supplied program.

Game Will Not Load.		You Are Either: Low On Memory
						Missing The Coin Mania Font
						AMOS Library Missing Or Old.

Not Able To Select Music.	Your Music Is Either In The Wrong Format, It
				Is Missing, Or You Are Low On Memory.

Not Able To Select SoundFX.	Your SoundFX File Is Missing Or You Are Low
				On Memory.

@EndNode
