    ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## #####    #####  ###### #####  ##  ## INSTALLATION

@{b}				--------------
				  Installing
                 "Coin Mania - A Bounce Into The Unknown"
  				 On Hard Disk
                                --------------
@{ub}
To Install "Coin Mania" On Your Hard Disk  Please Use The  Supplied Hard Disk
Installer.If You Encounter Problems Installing "Coin Mania" On Your Hard Disk
Then Please Write Back To Us With A Brief Explanation Of What Is Not  Working
And A Brief Description Of Your Setup i.e  Your Memory And Hardware Add-Ons.

@EndNode
@Node "GameFiles" "Coinmania.Guide/Game Files"

       #####  ####   #   #   #####    ##### ###### ##      #####  #####
      ##     ##  ## ### ### ##       ##       ##   ##     ##     ##
      ## ### ###### ####### ######   ######   ##   ##     ######  #### 
      ##  ## ##  ## ## # ## ##       ##       ##   ##  ## ##         ##
      ###### ##  ## ##   ## ######   ##     ###### ###### ###### ######
      ###### ##  ## ##   ## ######   ##     ###### ###### ###### ######
       ##### ##  ## ##   ##  #####   ##     ######  ####   ##### ##### 

This Is A  Comprehensive List Of All The Files Required By Coin Mania For It
To Work Correctly, So If The Game Refuses To  Work Then Check That All These
Files Exist.

   Banks/GameB.BANK           - Bobs Required For The Game
   Banks/HelpB.BANK           - Bobs Required For The Help Page
   Banks/MenuB.BANK           - Bobs Required For The Mein Menu
   Banks/MenuI.BANK           - Icons Required For The Main Menu

   Sounds/Intro.MUSIC         - Music Required For The Title Picture
   Sounds/InGame.MUSIC        - Music Played When Music InGame Selected
   Sounds/EndGame.MUSIC       - Music Played When Game Completed
   Sounds/High.MUSIC          - Hi-Score Table Music
   Sounds/Coinmania.SFX       - Normal Sound Effects For InGame
   Sounds/Coinmania.ESFX      - Sound Effects When Extra Memory Detected

   Data/CMAbout1.PAK          - BackGround Picture For The ABOUT Pages
   Data/CMAbout2.PAK          - BackGround Picture For The ABOUT Pages
   Data/CMTitlePage.PAK       - The Title Picture For Coin Mania
   Data/CMExtraMem.PAK        - The Extra Memory Picture
   Data/CMCongratulations.PAK - Picture Shown When Game Completed
@EndNode
@Node "CheapWare" "Coinmania.Guide/CheapWare"

