CheapWare Is A Name Given To Software That Is Sold Very Cheaply.  But Unlike
ShareWare  There  Are No Updates For Definate, But We Will If There Is A Big
Response To The  Game. If We Do Upgrade The Game Then It Will Be An Entirely
New Version Which You Can Upgrade To For A Reduced Fee If You Have Purchased
A Previous Version.

    So To See Upgrades To The Game. BUY IT, And Maybe We Will Release A

                             #################
                             # Coin Mania II #
                             #################
@EndNode
@Node "GameMenuTxt" "Coinmania/Guide/GameMenu"

       #####  ####   #   #   #####         #   #   ##### #####  ##  ##
      ##     ##  ## ### ### ##            ### ### ##     ##  ## ##  ##
      ## ### ###### ####### ######        ####### ###### ##  ## ##  ##
      ##  ## ##  ## ## # ## ##            ## # ## ##     ##  ## ##  ##
      ###### ##  ## ##   ## ######        ##   ## ###### ##  ## ######
      ###### ##  ## ##   ## ######        ##   ## ###### ##  ## ######
       ##### ##  ## ##   ##  #####        ##   ##  ##### ##  ##  ####

  @{B}ABOUT@{ub} ------------- About Who Wrote The Game And Greets To People We Know.
  @{B}HELP@{ub} -------------- About The Various Objects In The Game eg Arrows.
  @{B}MUSIC@{ub} ------------- When Enabled Music Plays Ingame.
  @{B}SOUNDFX@{ub} ----------- When Enabled Sound Effects Are Used Ingame.
  @{B}FILTER@{ub} ------------ When Selected Turns The Filter On/Off
  @{b}PLAYERS@{ub} ----------- Selecting This Selects Either One Or Two Players.
 @{b}@{" SEE HIGHSCORES " Link "HighScores"}@{ub} --- Displays The Days Highest Score Plus Top 5 Scores.
 @{b}@{" LEVEL CODE " Link "LevelCode"}@{ub} ------- Enter A Code Here To Start On A Different Level.
  @{b}LEVEL LOAD@{ub} -------- Load In Your Own Levels Designed With The Level Editor.
  @{b}START THE GAME@{ub} ---- The Most Important Menu Item. Start The Game From Here.

To Pause The Game Whilst Playing It, Press "P" On The  Keyboard,  To  Resume,
Press "Fire" on Your Joystick.  If "Esc" Is Pressed,  This  Will  Abort  Your
Current Game.
@EndNode
@Node "HighScores" "Coinmania/Guide/HighScores"

     ##  ## ######  ##### ##  ##  #####  ####   ####  #####   #####  #####
     ##  ##   ##   ##     ##  ## ##     ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##     ##
     ######   ##   ## ### ######  ####  ##     ##  ## ###### ######  #### 
     ##  ##   ##   ##  ## ##  ##     ## ##  ## ##  ## ## ##  ##         ##
     ##  ## ###### ###### ##  ## ###### ###### ###### ##  ## ###### ######
     ##  ## ###### ###### ##  ## ###### ###### ###### ##  ## ###### ######
     ##  ## ######  ##### ##  ## #####   ####   ####  ##  ##  ##### ##### 
 
 On The Highscore Screen When You Are Asked To:

			@{b}"Depress Fire To Continue"@{ub}

Move The Joystick  Either Left Or Right And Press Fire  And You Can Load Or
Save Highscores So You Can Take Them Over To A  Friends House And Load Them
Into Their Copy Of The Game To Compare Scores.

@EndNode

@Node "LevelCode" "Coinmania/Guide/LevelCode"

     ##      ##### ##  ##  ##### ##            ####   ####  #####   #####
     ##     ##     ##  ## ##     ##           ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##
     ##     ###### ##  ## ###### ##           ##     ##  ## ##  ## ######
     ##  ## ##     ##  ## ##     ##  ##       ##  ## ##  ## ##  ## ##
     ###### ###### ###### ###### ######       ###### ###### ###### ######
     ###### ######  ####  ###### ######       ###### ###### ###### ######
      ####   #####   ##    #####  ####         ####   ####  #####   #####

On This Screen You  Can Enter Seperate Level Codes For The Different Players
But  Only If Both Players  Are Playing, ie If You Have Selected A Two Player
Game. To  Enter A Code Move The Red Box Onto Either:

				 @{b}"PLAYER 1"@{ub}

				     Or

				 @{b}"PLAYER 2"@{ub}

And Press Fire. Once The Codes Are Correct Then Move The Red Box To The Box
At The Bottom And Press Fire.

@EndNode
